{
  "stem": "18575.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 387.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got a, I would say, piece of bread that would be quarter pound, a little more than quarter pound and, twice a day, soup, a soup in the lunch time and a soup at night-- very thin soup, watery soup, no potatoes.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the-- the-- the food, but there was no persecution.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was-- they were-- left us alone, more or less.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "After four weeks, I was assigned to an electric kommando.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Buna was a camp attached to IG Farben factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "IG Farben was the world's largest chemical factory-- in fact, associated with American Exxon-- today Exxon, but the old Esso.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They build a-- the prisoners built it-- a factory producing synthetic rubber and synthetic oil.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was attached to the kommando number 141.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My kapo was a German Jew from Hamburg, a young boy who already spent several years in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His name is Leon-- Leo Ziegler--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Z-I-E-G-L-E-R-- very nice, very kind guy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only became kapo because of his long term in prison.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he was-- and he spoke fluent German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, he was German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The kommando was attached to a power station, high voltage power, to build control cells controlling the switching of the electrical power to the different processing plants that they had.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My job was to wire those from drawings, from schematics.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Being sufficiently intelligent, I could read the schematics.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And watching others, I very fast picked up the wiring of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The nice things about it was that while you work, the SS, who was parading back and forth, would not touch you.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because the-- your bosses were German mechanics, German foremen who are responsible for the wiring.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But if you did something that was-- they considered sabotage, you were executed in camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
